{{Quote|Gamorrean snack crackers are ''my'' favorite, but you'll need an Anoat malted to duck them in.|[[Sligh]]|<ref name="Fate of the Jedi: Ascension">''[[Fate of the Jedi: Ascension]]''</ref>}}
A '''Gamorrean snack-cracker''' was a kind of food item in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. It was worth roughly one credit. Gamorrean snack-crackers were sometimes eaten after being dunked in [[Anoat malted]]s.

==Appearances==
